@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 13
title 图19  订单状态流转图

[*] --> PENDING_PAYMENT : 创建订单 (expiresAt = +15min)
PENDING_PAYMENT --> PAID : 模拟支付成功
PENDING_PAYMENT --> CANCELLED : 用户主动取消
PENDING_PAYMENT --> EXPIRED : 倒计时超时 (调度任务)
PAID --> REFUNDED : 自助退票(开演前 2h+) / 管理员退款

note right of PENDING_PAYMENT
  座位 LOCKED / 区域库存 locked
end note

note right of PAID
  座位 SOLD / 区域 sold, 票据 UNUSED
end note

note right of EXPIRED
  释放座位锁 / 回补区域库存, 票据置 VOID
end note

PAID --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]
EXPIRED --> [*]
REFUNDED --> [*]
@enduml
